      "id": "5a93c517_1e6e0930",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/sdnc/templates/ueb-deployment.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 1,
      "message": "UEB is really the SDC interface that uses SDC client to get authentication credentials, receive/reply NOTIFY, DOWNLOAD, DEPLOY_OK per the SDC protocol. dmaap-listener simply subscribes and update dbhost upon a event on the topic. Besides the functional difference the design is to have a container per subscription. SDNC team may create more complex listeners in the future but it made more sense to keep these two functions separate since there is little overlap in code.",
